Spark-cassandra-connector
https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/com.datastax.spark/spark-cassandra-connector

Password ssh for mac
https://phoenixnap.com/kb/setup-passwordless-ssh

connector
spark-submit --packages com.datastax.spark:spark-cassandra-connector_2.12:2.5.0

Add this line to $SPARK_HOME/conf/spark-defaults.conf.template
spark.jars.packages     com.datastax.spark:spark-cassandra-connector_2.11:3.3.0

╰─λ spark-submit --master spark://Aryans-MacBook-Air.local:7077 --packages com.datastax.spark:spark-cassandra-connector_2.12:3.3.0 batch_processing/batch_process.py

